GOAL
--------------------------------------------------

Develop a complete internal Data Updater Portal used by manufacturing and sales teams to manage operational data.

The portal should allow Data Updaters to:

• Manage Products
• Manage Categories
• Manage Industries
• Manage Resources
• Manage FAQs
• Manage Gallery
• Process RFQs
• Prepare Quotations
• Update Orders
• Update Production Status
• Update Shipment Information
• Upload Customer Documents
• Manage Customer-visible Content

All business logic must reuse existing services.

